urn:uuid:83f5fc0b-582b-4074-ae70-49a551b.summary: <![CDATA[ <img hspace="5" src="https://ocdn.eu/sport-images-transforms/1/g7Jk9lBaHR0cHM6Ly9vY2RuLmV1L3B1bHNjbXMvTURBXy85NGM4MmQwNTQzYWQ5ODIyYjM1NTQxMTE2ZDdkNTEzMi5qcGeTlQPNAyIzzQlGzQU2kwXNBQDNAtCTCaZkNDFkOGMG3gACoTABoTEB" align="right" />US Open wystartowało z przytupem.
